title: cppbot.package.1.01-miniyou
description:
Name: CppBot Package 1.01
Sys req: Win 98 or newer
Company: None, credz to various groups
Price: $0, it&#039;s just a package of free software




This is a package of three programs used
for improving the gaming experience of
Maplestory. The programs are
-CppBot
-DXwnd
-Injec-TOR
and contains several popular tools such as
AutoChat, AutoLoot and AutoClick.
Instructions are found in ReadMe.txt after
installation




Originally released on TPB by miniyou,
but I couldn&#039;t care less about what you do
with it as long as you keep seeding until
you have a nice ratio.
